{
 "file": "_STGSP2B.bin",
 "source_size": 27036,
 "built_size": 29075,
 "edits": [
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a5e",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看到了！是布鲁塞尔的总统府！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6e7d7e7baef97e7b6e831e8a2e950e7e1e7b4e881e929ea60ef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a8d",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "全舰、进入第1种战斗配置！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb4e7d402e892e891e940eff7e7d1ef28e7ffea34ea0eef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a9a",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "作战目标、击破敌方MS部队！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2fef28efd4e96f02e7ccef6de7e3efb1efa7ef9eef70e7c9ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1aab",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "敌方战力被压制后、便突入总统府、救出{00}次官！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e3efb1ef28efb0e7f1e992e8dee7fe02e8fae8b6e891e881e929ea6002e8caefbe00e864ef92ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1aed",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "愚蠢的家伙……竟打算与我们顽抗到底吗",
   "zh_hex": "15e959e94be7b4e7dfe7fd0909ef2ce7f5e889e832efcce7bbeafae912e7d7e9b4e80200000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b1d",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "明明就算毁掉MS、也休想攻破这座避难{00}所",
   "zh_hex": "15ef39ef39e7c5e889e97ce9d3efa7ef9e02e7c0e90ee7e6ef67ef6de7b9ebc4efd9e86600e7fb000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b3a",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……说到底、不过是徒劳的挣扎罢了",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7ede7d7e9b402e7b5ef36e7b6eb02ec4ae7b4ebcae84beaefe7ba00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b9c",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "全员、战斗开始！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb4e84902ef28e7ffe7fae908ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bcd",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶、是增援吗！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7de02e7b6ea3de863e802ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bf4",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "各机、别打乱队形！一旦被敌人的数量吞{00}没、可就完了！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e819e7e402e7e5e7f5e976e7c9ec670687ebcde7f1e7e3b4e7b4e914e851ed3200e7d802e7c4e7c5e87ee7ba060600000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c3e",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶！又来敌人了！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7deef97e8f1efcfe7e3efb2e7baef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c71",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我不说再见、杰克斯",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcce7b5e7ede80be85c02e8ebe7d5e7c8000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c9d",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是自然！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6efb5e7efef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ca4",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我也知道是乱来……可不做到这个份上、{00}谁都没法站起来反抗！",
   "zh_hex": "158be7c0e85ae82ae7b6e976d90909e7c4e7b5e81ce7d7e7b9e828ea22b20200e923e840e7d8e84eec31e847d9e87ce91206000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ce5",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您是在等待吧……杰克斯",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e7b6ef29e826eaa8e7d00909e8ebe7d5e7c80000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d11",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "没错！等待那些、渴望和平的人们！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d8e885ef97e826eaa8e7b7e8a402ed84e965e7d3e887e7b4efb2e7bbef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d25",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "如果这个地球、就这样放过玛莉梅亚……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f0e871e7b9e828bf9502e7c5e7b9e7dae86cef36e845e81ee9f2e7d6090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d3b",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那只会催生出第二个米利亚尔特·匹斯克{00}拉福特！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7ef32e7e2ed22b6afe940ea13e828e878e82ee7d6e7e1e7cf04ed2ae7c8e7d500e7c2ea7ce7cf060600000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d7c",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯……我们绝不能就此放弃！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8650909efcce7bbe91ce7b5e7c6e7c5e7cae86ce938ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d8d",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "坚信和平、并为之战斗……",
   "zh_hex": "15eb80e90fe7d3e88702e957e7c1e7cdef28e7ff09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d9a",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "因为那、就是我们唯一能够做到的事！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef33e7c1e7b702e7c5e7b6efcce7bbea89efb6e7c6e920e81ce7d7e7b4efb8ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1dd9",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……真是一群不肯死心的人呢",
   "zh_hex": "150909e820e7b6efb6ecfae7b5e93def6ae82de7b4efb2e907000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1dea",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "明明胜负、早就已经分晓了……{00}不得不说、真是愚蠢至极",
   "zh_hex": "15ef39ef39e8dbe92c02e963e7c5ef3ae8b7cdec73e7ba090900e7b5e80ae7b5e7ed02e820e7b6e959e94be897eaca0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e33",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcc09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e58",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您怎么了、莉莉娜小姐？",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e7f2e7bde7ba02e81ee81ee7eae83ee9210500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e81",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我、一直都在逃避……！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcc02efb6e875e840ef29e8c2efd90909ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ec2",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ee1",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『自称玛莉梅雅军的部队、与联邦军之间{00}爆发的战斗……』",
   "zh_hex": "150cefb5ea01e845e81ee9f2ebfde7e0e7b4ef70e7c902e832ef2eefaae7e0e7cde8fc00ef84e870e7b4ef28e7ff09090d0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f6d",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『屏幕前的各位观众！』",
   "zh_hex": "150ced4eec14ef51e7b4e819e834eaf2eafbef970d000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f93",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哦哦、那是……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e919e91902e7b7e7b60909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fed",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『请大家、千万不要对眼前这光景感到畏{00}惧！』",
   "zh_hex": "150ce83aefa5e7df02eafde9f8e7b5ef2ae7bee90bef51e7b9e83dec21e87de7d7ecf000ec6eef970d0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2019",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嚯……",
   "zh_hex": "15e9dd09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x206c",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『和平、绝不是别人能够赐予的东西！！{00}』",
   "zh_hex": "150ce7d3e88702e91ce7b5e7b6e7e5efb2e7c6e920eff2efb7e7b4e8bae7f8ef97ef97000d00000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x209f",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……又、又要打仗了吗？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8f102e8f1ef2ae7f5ea37e7bae802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20d0",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "没事、夏克蒂",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d8a902ef37e7d5e9f5000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20de",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不会演变成战争的……一定不会",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7e2ea2fe955e837ef28e852e7b40909efb6e867e7b5e7e2000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x210c",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『并非由谁来赐予、而是要凭自己的双手{00}……』",
   "zh_hex": "150ce957e8f0e8a6e923efcfeff2efb702e89ce7b6ef2aea49efb5e8c9e7b4eabcef660009090d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2182",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您登场、还为时尚早呢……女王陛下",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e9a0e87602e7f7e7c1ef2deccee963e9070909efade884eb24ef4d00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21da",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "宣扬完全和平的女王、却要驱使民众去战{00}斗吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15ecccebc6e87eefb4e7d3e887e7b4efade88402eadfef2aebffe83fef38eafbe7ebef2800e7ffe8020500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2212",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我、已经不再是匹斯克拉福特家的人了",
   "zh_hex": "15efcc02ef3ae8b7e7b5e80be7b6ed2ae7c8e7d5e7c2ea7ce7cfe7dfe7b4efb2e7ba00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2222",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们需要的、并非主义或主张、而是那颗{00}渴望和平的心",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe92def2ae7b402e957e8f0e954e8cee905e954eac502e89ce7b6e7b7eec700ed84e965e7d3e887e7b4e82d00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2242",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我之所以回到多利安家、正是因为明白了{00}这一点",
   "zh_hex": "158be7cde7fbe7f38ce7d7e7e9e82ee7fce7df02ef3be7b6ef33e7c1ef39e809e7ba00e7b987e822000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x227b",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你是说、民众会为了和平、自发地行动起{00}来？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b6e7ed02ef38eafbe7e2e7c1e7bae7d3e88702efb5e870ef63efd6ef30e84700efcf0500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x228d",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你果然、还是不配做这统领世界的女王呢",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e871e7ef02e7f7e7b6e7b5ea34e81ce7b9e929ea20e83ce8f5e7b4efade884e907000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22cf",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你看……好好瞧着吧、你那些同伴、马上{00}就要全军覆灭了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7f60909e7c7e7c7ead4e86de7d002e7b8e7b7e8a4e85dea7202e84fef4c00e7c5ef2aefb4e7e0ee9ce8e1e7ba00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22eb",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "然后、成为胜者的、就是我",
   "zh_hex": "15e7efe7fe02e837e7c1e8dbef6ee7b402e7c5e7b6efcc0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2316",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "人们那颗渴望和平的心、是无法用武力来{00}压制的……",
   "zh_hex": "15efb2e7bbe7b7eec7ed84e965e7d3e887e7b4e82d02e7b6e7dce84eefb3e8ecefb0efcf00e992e8dee7b409090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2339",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……没错、我对此深信不疑",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7d8e88502efcce7bee7caeb0de90fe7b5eb62000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x236e",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "MS、MS部队……已经全军覆没了……",
   "zh_hex": "15efa7ef9e02efa7ef9eef70e7c90909ef3ae8b7efb4e7e0ee9ce7d8e7ba09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x239a",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎、怎么可能……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f202e7f2e7bde7c4e7c60909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23da",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！上、上空有敌机突入！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def97ef4c02ef4ce93fe7cbe7e3e7e4e8b6e891ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23ed",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是飞翼零式！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6ea45ec35eb74ea26ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2414",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2440",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……开始确认",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7fae908e88ce8a00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2449",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "护盾展开了吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8e0eb63e989e7fae7bae7d00500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2476",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你、你这家伙、想干什么……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b802e7b8e7b9e7dfe7fd02e7e6e8d3e7dde7bd0909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x249f",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "避难所、确实完好无损吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15efd9e866e7fb02e88ce87fe87ee7c7e7dcea28e7d005000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24c8",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是自然、好好认清你们自己的无力吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6efb5e7ef02e7c7e7c7e8a0e995e7b8e7bbefb5e8c9e7b4e7dcefb0e7d00000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24f8",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……了解",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7bae89d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2526",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就、就凭这点攻击、岂能打破护盾！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c502e7c5ea49e7b9e822ef67e7cc02eac3e7c6e7f5ef6de8e0eb63ef97ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x255a",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "真、真是个可悲的家伙……",
   "zh_hex": "15e82002e820e7b6e828e7c4e9dfe7b4e7dfe7fd09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2569",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "明明做这种事、根本毫无意义……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef39ef39e81ce7b9e7d1efb802e9b8efa6ea0ae7dcef3ce8ce090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2596",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……害怕了吗？玛莉梅亚",
   "zh_hex": "150909e988e958e7bae80205e845e81ee9f2e7d6000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25be",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def970909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x261f",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呜哦！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d9e919ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2643",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "护、护盾强度减半！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8e002e8e0eb63e8ade96ded24eadeef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x266f",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为、为何会这样……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c102e7c1efbce7e2e7b9e7da0909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x269a",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "飞翼零式的攻击、{00}误差竟不到0.2秒！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea45ec35eb74ea26e7b49ee7cc0200ea33e9c7ef2ce7b5e7d7e998e0020fee79060600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26b9",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "要是同一个地方、{00}再被攻击一次的话……！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ae7b6e85d87e828bfd00200e80be7f19ee7cc87e864e7b4e81f09090600000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2742",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "避难所、它……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efd9e866e7fb02e9780909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2766",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "被打破了……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f1e7f5ef6de7ba090905000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2796",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "德、德基姆大人！",
   "zh_hex": "15e82c02e82ce829e823beb4060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27bb",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎、怎么了！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f202e7f2e7bde7baef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27e0",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "总统府前、聚集了大批民众！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e881e929ea60ba02ebe8ea98e7babeed63ef38eafb060600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27ee",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊、不！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c302e7b5ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27f6",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我军占领的各处、市民们都纷纷涌了过来{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7e0eb51ea20e7b4e819e90302ebc3ef38e7bbe840ecf8ecf8ed82e7baef36efcf00ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2830",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什、什么……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dd02e7dde7bd0909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2878",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我、我们、才不会向军队的威胁低头呢！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcc02efcce7bb02e836e7b5e7e2efc1e7e0e7c9e7b4e96bedadec08e92ee907ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28af",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我已经受够战争了！",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef3ae8b7e8c8e920ef28e852e7baef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28dc",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们的和平、由我们自己来守护！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe7b4e7d3e88702e8a6efcce7bbefb5e8c9efcfe8a8e8e0ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x292f",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这、这是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b902e7b9e7b60909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2961",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那、正是你错了的证据",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b702ef3be7b6e7b8e885e7bae7b4eba3e8cc000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2994",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "玛莉梅亚大人",
   "zh_hex": "15e845e81ee9f2e7d6beb400000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29b6",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你、你是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b802e7b8e7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29da",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您的父亲、特列斯阁下他……",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e7b4e888e89402e7cfe8b5e7c8e8d7ef4de80c0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29eb",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "始终深爱着那些、纵然屡战屡败、也绝不{00}放弃战斗意志的人们",
   "zh_hex": "15e908e8e2eb0de8d5e86de7b7e8a402e8e6e7efee13ef28ee13e88f02e7c0e91ce7b500e86ce938ef28e7ffef3cea18e7b4efb2e7bb00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a0a",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "能够打动人心的、从来都不是胜者",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c6e920e7f5ef30efb2e82de7b402e88aefcfe840e7b5e7b6e8dbef6e00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a3d",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可、可是我……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c402e7c4e7b6efcc09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a48",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "成为胜者……继承父亲的遗志……",
   "zh_hex": "15e837e7c1e8dbef6e0909e9d6ea75e888e894e7b4eba9ea1809090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a78",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "快些醒悟过来吧、玛莉梅亚",
   "zh_hex": "15e85fe8a4eb20ea19ef36d9e7d002e845e81ee9f2e7d6000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2aa3",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "莉、莉莉娜……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81e02e81ee81ee7ea0909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ac8",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你、已经懂得了什么叫恐惧……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b802ef3ae8b7e8b0e80ae7bae7dde7bde8c1eb33ec6e0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2adc",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "也正因如此、你才能够承认自己的过错",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c0ef3bef33e7f0e7ca02e7b8e836e7c6e920ea75e8a0efb5e8c9e7b4ef36e88500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b18",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我的过错……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b4ef36e88509090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b3c",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "够了、都给我闭嘴！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e920e7ba02e840e839efccebabeae2ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b8b",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你这家伙！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b9e7dfe7fdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2bad",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们巴顿一族、才是地球圈真正的支配者{00}！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe85bedc7efb6eb5e02e836e7b6ef63efd3e9fbe820ef3be7b4e883ea34ef6e00ef97ef970000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2bcb",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "别再往我的玛莉梅亚脑子里、塞这些蠢话{00}！臭女人！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e5e80be9118be7b4e845e81ee9f2e7d6eb67e886ef3102e950e7b9e8a4e94be81f0006ecfdb0b406060000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c0e",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不要啊！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef2ae7c3ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c69",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "玛莉梅亚！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e845e81ee9f2e7d60605000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c98",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2cba",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "竟然去护着那女人……真是个愚蠢的孩子",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ce7efe7ebe8e0e86de7b7efadefb20909e820e7b6e828e959e94be7b4e956e8860000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ce9",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "德基姆、你这家伙！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e82ce829e82302e7b8e7b9e7dfe7fd060600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d0e",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽说玛莉梅亚的替身、要多少有多少……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7ede845e81ee9f2e7d6e7b4ea50e88d02ef2ae7e9b1e7cbe7e9b1090900000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d27",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可你们、把我的盘算一个接一个尽数推翻{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b8e7bb02e81b8be7b4ec2fe88987e828b787e828e8f2e914eaabe80800090900000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d43",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我非得、给你们一份相称的报应不可",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce8f0e80a02e839e7b8e7bbefb6ea22e8b1ea01e7b4e913e873e7b5e7c4000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d6e",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "去死吧！莉莉娜·多利安！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7eba7e7d006e81ee81ee7ea04e7e9e82ee7fc0606000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2dbb",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e37",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你、你这家……伙……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b802e7b8e7b9e7df0909e7fd0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e95",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……逆贼德基姆·巴顿、已被处决",
   "zh_hex": "150909eeb4eea6e82ce829e82304e85bedc702ef3ae7f1e903e8ab000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ea8",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就以此、为我背叛特列斯阁下一事、致以{00}歉意……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7f3e7ca02e7c1efcce9e4ef43e7cfe8b5e7c8e8d7ef4defb6efb802ea32e7f300e927ef3c090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f01",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f22",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "还疼吗、玛莉梅亚大人？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f7ecf1e80202e845e81ee9f2e7d6beb405000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f4c",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f52",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是吗……我、竟然活下来了呢",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e8020909efcc02ef2ce7efe8d4ef4defcfe7bae907000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f66",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def970909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f88",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你现在、还是先好好静养着为好",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e82fef2902e7f7e7b6ef8be7c7e7c7eab3ec0be86de7c1e7c70000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2fb6",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "莉莉娜小姐……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81ee81ee7eae83ee92109090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2fbf",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我、对你……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcc02e7bee7b809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3008",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我、我错了",
   "zh_hex": "15efcc02efcce885e7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3015",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……对不起",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7bee7b5e8470000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x303a",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "玛莉梅亚……",
   "zh_hex": "15e845e81ee9f2e7d609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3058",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "OZ残党的这场起事、看来是了结了",
   "zh_hex": "15ed1ceedae97bea73e7b4e7b9e876e847efb802e7f6efcfe7b6e7bae868e7ba00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x308b",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过话说回来、那个叫德基姆的家伙……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef36e81fe7ed8cd902e7b7e828e8c1e82ce829e823e7b4e7dfe7fd0909000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x30a3",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "居然能凑齐那么一支军队啊",
   "zh_hex": "15ea4ce7efe7c6ecb1e924e7b7e7bdefb6e883e7e0e7c9e7c300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x30d0",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这说明、如今仍有许多人、在拒绝和平、{00}渴求着战争吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7edef3902e7f0efb9eab9e7cbe8a7e7e9efb202ef29eb07e91ce7d3e8870200ed84e93ae86def28e852e7d00000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x310f",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "人们的意识、绝不是一时半刻、就能改变{00}的……",
   "zh_hex": "15efb2e7bbe7b4ef3ce92f02e91ce7b5e7b6efb6ef2deadee91f02e7c5e7c6e9f0e95500e7b409090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x312d",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "但经过这次的事件、人们想必、已经有所{00}领悟",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dbe8b7ef36e7b9e864e7b4efb8e99102efb2e7bbe7e6e86002ef3ae8b7e7cbe7fb00ea20ea190000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3147",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "领悟到、用自己的双手、去开创和平的那{00}份可贵……",
   "zh_hex": "15ea20ea19e7d702efb3efb5e8c9e7b4eabcef6602e7ebe7fae893e7d3e887e7b4e7b700ea22e7c4e93009090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x319f",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哼……和平、是吗",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b30909e7d3e88702e7b6e8020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x31ab",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "该打倒的敌人都不打倒、还算什么完全和{00}平……",
   "zh_hex": "15e898e7f5e848e7b4e7e3efb2e840e7b5e7f5e84802e7f7e889e7dde7bde87eefb4e7d300e88709090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x31ca",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "也罢、就让我好好地、从德基姆·巴顿的{00}失败里吸取教训吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c0eaef02e7c5e7f98be7c7e7c7bf02e88ae82ce829e82304e85bedc7e7b400e8a5e88fef31ed34e987eaacec3ce7d0000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x31ec",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……学一学、该如何才能不重蹈他的失败",
   "zh_hex": "150909eb55efb6eb5502e898e7f0efbce836e7c6e7b5e8a1eeaee80ce7b4e8a5e88f0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6276",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "竟、竟然到此为止……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2c02ef2ce7efe7d7e7cae7c1e86909090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6302",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一路辛苦了",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6e8d2ea58e9e6e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x630f",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "感谢你将这条『宇宙世纪路线』一路游玩{00}到了最后",
   "zh_hex": "15e87de8b2e7b8e84ae7b9e9d40ce8bee8bfe83ceb99e8d2e9160defb6e8d2ea94e97000e7d7e7bae8c5e7fe000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x632f",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另外、隆德·贝尔队的征战、就先在此告{00}一段落了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e99be8f702ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e7b4ecd2ef2802e7c5ef8bef29e7cae8e500efb6ea6be92ae7ba09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x634e",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过游戏本身仍可继续下去、今后也请你{00}继续尽情享受",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef36ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9adef4de7eb02efb9e7fee7c0e83ae7b800e9d6e9ade8f2e88bec06e8c800000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6373",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另外、为一路通关本路线的你、还专门准{00}备了一个特别关卡",
   "zh_hex": "15e99be8f702e7c1efb6e8d2ef59e8bbefa6e8d2e916e7b4e7b802e7f7eb4be90ce87a00e877e7baefb6e828e7cfe7e5e8bbe8010000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x639a",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是和我们分头作战、一直战斗至今的大{00}天使队之间的特别演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e7d3efcce7bbefaee92eef2fef2802efb6e875ef28e7ffe897efb9e7b4efa500e844e83fe7c9e7cde8fce7b4e7cfe7e5ea2feab6000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x63bb",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "和他们交手一番、亲自检验你培养至今的{00}部队实力、也是件好事",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d3e80ce7bbe861ef66efb6ee6d02e894efb5ee40ea99e7b8edfeec0be897efb9e7b400ef70e7c9e87fefb002e7c0e7b6e991e7c7efb8000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x63e0",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特殊演习』、便能与{00}他们一决高下",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29abe8a6e7beef28c0e966eaaa0ce7cfed7bea2feab60d02e8fae7c6e83200e80ce7bb87e8abe812890000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6405",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、就请继续游玩『SD高达G世{00}代DS』吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd02e7c5e83ae9d6e9adea94e9700cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83c00e8e7ef96ef9e0de7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6429",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后也希望你能静下心来、尽情玩到最后",
   "zh_hex": "15efb9e7fee7c0e87be965e7b8e7c6eab3ef4de82defcf02e8f2e88be970e7d7e8c5e7fe00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x64a2",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "谢谢你一路以来、一直陪着我这个不太靠{00}得住的舰长",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b2e8b2e7b8efb6e8d2e7f3efcf02efb6e875ef42e86defcce7b9e828e7b5e86ae8c700e80ae859e7b4e7d4ef34000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x64c1",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『平成高达路线』、就到此告一段落{00}了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce887e837e812ef2be8d2e9160d02e7c5e7d7e7cae8e5efb6ea6be92a00e7ba000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x64df",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽说、我们预防者的这场战斗、是已经结{00}束了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7ed02efcce7bbea5ae968ef6ee7b4e7b9e876ef28e7ff02e7b6ef3ae8b7e86800e895e7ba090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x64f9",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不过游戏本身也还能继续下去哦、今{00}后也请你继续享受游戏吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b5ef36ea94ea3eefa6e88de7c0e7f7e7c6e9d6e9adef4de7ebe91902efb900e7fee7c0e83ae7b8e9d6e9adec06e8c8ea94ea3ee7d000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x651f",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为一路玩通这条路线的你、还另外准备了{00}全新的关卡哦",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1efb6e8d2e970ef59e7b9e9d4e8d2e916e7b4e7b802e7f7e99be8f7e87ae877e7ba00efb4ef8ae7b4e8bbe801e91900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6543",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是与我们分头、和提坦斯及新吉翁交过{00}手的……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e8328be7bbcde92e02e7d3e821e843e7c8e9cfef8ae7d9ee88e861ef3600aee7b40909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x655e",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……正是和那支隆德·贝尔队之间的特别{00}演习哦",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef3be7b6e7d3e7b7e883ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e7cde8fce7b4e7cfe7e500ea2feab6e919000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6571",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特别演习』、就能和{00}他们一战了哦",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efb5e8a6e7beef28ef4ee966eaaa0ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d02e7c5e7c6e7d300e80ce7bbefb6ef28e7bae9190000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6597",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请务必挑战看看哦",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae94fe860eae7ef28e7f6e7f6e919000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x65a5",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、就请继续游玩『SD高达G世{00}代DS』吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd02e7c5e83ae9d6e9adea94e9700cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83c00e8e7ef96ef9e0de7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x65c9",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『自由对战的战火！尽情冲杀吧、大天使{00}号！！』",
   "zh_hex": "150cefb5e8a6e7beef28e7b4ef28e8daef97e8f2e88be95ee89be7d002efa5e844e83f00e833ef97ef970d0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x664a",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是主天使号的舰长、娜塔尔·巴基露露{00}中佐",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6e954e844e83fe833e7b4e7d4ef3402e7eae945e7e1ef4be85be829e858e85800ef4eefba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x665a",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "首先、请允许我向你一路以来出色的指挥{00}致以由衷的敬意",
   "zh_hex": "15ef40b802e83aecade8a78b9de7b887e8d2e7f3d9afe89fe7b4e8c0e94900ea32e7f3e8a6edb3e7b4ee38ef3c00000000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x667c",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正是多亏了你的协助、我们才终于得以奋{00}战到最后",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3be7b6e7e9eab7e7bae7b8e7b4e8f6ea2302efcce7bbe836e8e2e879e80ae7f3ef4600ef28e7d7e8c5e7fe0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x669e",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『对手路线』、就到此结束了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce7beef66e8d2e9160d02e7c5e7d7e7cae868e895e7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x66b4",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽说、我们主天使队的这场战斗、是已经{00}到此结束了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7ed02efcce7bbe954e844e83fe7c9e7b4e7b9e876ef28e7ff02e7b6ef3ae8b700e7d7e7cae868e895e7ba090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x66cd",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过游戏本身仍可继续下去、今后也请你{00}继续尽情享受",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef36ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9adef4de7eb02efb9e7fee7c0e83ae7b800e9d6e9ade8f2e88bec06e8c800000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x66f1",
   "jp_len": 43,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "自由对战今后仍可继续下去、另外、只要{00}选择『特别演习』……",
   "zh_hex": "15efb5e8a6e7beef28efb9e7feeab9e7c4e9d6e9adef4de7eb02e99be8f702ef32ef2a00e966eaaa0ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x671c",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "便能与隆德·贝尔、预防者一同进行一场{00}联合演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e8fae7c6e832ed16e82cef4be857e7e102ea5ae968ef6eefb6e85de892efd6efb6e87600ef2eefc0ea2feab60000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x673a",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我坚信、以你的本领、在与他们的战斗中{00}也定能克敌制胜",
   "zh_hex": "15efcceb80e90f02e7f3e7b8e7b4efa6ea2002ef29e832e80ce7bbe7b4ef28e7ffef4e00e7c0e867e7c6e7d5e7e3e8dee8db000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x675f",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、就请继续游玩『SD高达G世{00}代DS』吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd02e7c5e83ae9d6e9adea94e9700cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83c00e8e7ef96ef9e0de7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6783",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后也愿你武运长久、奋战不息",
   "zh_hex": "15efb9e7fee7c0e961e7b8e8ece986ef34e9db02ef46ef28e7b5ec6a000000"
  }
 ]
}
